<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="balance-n">balance <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'bæləns/    美 /'bæləns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1c">1.<strong>[C] 天平；秤：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Weigh it on the balance. 
在秤/天平上称它的重量。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] [常用单数] 平衡；均衡：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>keep / lose one’s balance</strong>
保持/失去平衡</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Athletes need a good <strong>sense of balance</strong>.
运动员要有良好的平衡感。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I think it’s important to have <strong>a balance between</strong> study and a social life, so I’m going to join a few clubs.
我认为保持学习和社交的平衡很重要，所以打算参加几个俱乐部。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 5</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[常用单数] 余额；余款：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have a balance of about $50,000 in my savings account. 
我的存款账户里有五万美元左右的余额。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They were due to pay the balance on delivery.
他们须将余款在到货时付清。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-balance">on balance</h3>
<p>1.<strong>总的说来</strong><br />
after considering all the information：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On balance, I think we made the right decision.
总的来说，我认为我们做的决定是正确的。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>When he was running after his brother, the boy lost his <strong><em>_</em></strong> and had a bad fall.  （2015 湖北改）  </li>
<li>I’ve got a good sense of <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (平衡) and learnt to ski quite quickly.  （2013 陕西）  </li>
<li>You are working too hard. You’d better <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (保持平衡) between work and relaxation.   （2012 天津改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. balance  2. balance  3. keep a balance   </p></div>